{"tid":1890043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（注意）確診58歲的士司機揸JW9897 曾到大埔診所求醫","createTime":"2020-02-21T03:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T07:55:33.000Z","uid":240448,"like":102,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"c98b5625729421c4b8d71d287d5c12f7e0406aac","tid":1890043,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"第二宗確診個案涉及一名58歲男病人（為第68宗個案）。病人過往健康良好，居於元朗新田石湖圍。他自二月八日起出現發燒和咳嗽，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">於二月十日及二月十七日向同一名私家醫生求診(大埔昌運一間診所）。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他於二月十八日到北區醫院求醫，昨日因昏厥而入住該院接受治療。他的呼吸道樣本證實對2019冠狀病毒病病毒呈陽性反應，現時情況穩定。病人於潛伏期內沒有外遊，其同住的妻子及兒子沒有出現病徵，將被安排接受檢疫。<br />\n <br />\n　　病人為一名市區的士司機，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他駕駛的的士車牌號碼為JW9897</span></span>，最後上班日期為二月十六日。曾於一月二十五日至二月十六日期間乘搭該的士的乘客，請致電衞生防護中心熱線。"},{"pid":"18c025c130b57c638d30fce54924ccfef6a114bc","tid":1890043,"uid":240448,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VD2Txk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VD2Txk.png&h=b1aa6ade&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33VEbi0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33VEbi0.png&h=9161a6c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79ec47a61b93ac2399da08eb5141dc16ceabfc9d","tid":1890043,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:09:30.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395e7cc838071440dc7311b9a4090b5cc5443e04","tid":1890043,"uid":64576,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"主要做邊區先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4eae27862446b95ff983f6eae25216e7b231c6b","tid":1890043,"uid":240448,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"395e7cc838071440dc7311b9a4090b5cc5443e04","tid